snippet.title: Vendetta Online Gameplay
snippet.description:
http://mmo-play.com/rpg-games/vendetta-online to watch more videos, view screenshots and read Vendetta Online review. Subscribe to http://MMO-Play.com channel for more gaming videos: http://bit.ly/UtS47X

Vendetta Online is sci-fi MMORPG, developed and published by Guild Software. released in 2004, Vendetta Online features PvP and PvE contents and has a great gameplay.
